         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne bot. Garden ¶ 3/6/70 ¶ Sir ¶  ¶ I have the honor to express my best thanks for your goodness of providing for the repayments of the one hundred and fifty pounds, which two years ago I paid o...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">70.06.03a<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; "/>
            </p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To James McCulloch<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">W70/6236, unit 466, VPRS 3991/P inward registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; ">Trans. Angela. To proof.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>Melbourne bot. Garden</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">3/6/70</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have the honor to express my best thanks for your goodness of providing for the repayments of the one hundred and fifty pounds, which two years ago I paid out of my slender private means, to effect then at once the transfer of the Dromedaries to the Queensland Government without any accumulating costs.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>M had last asked for reimbursement in M to J. MacPherson, 13 January 1870, having previously requested it more than once<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(see M to J. MacPherson, 25 October 1869 (in this edition as 69-10-25a)). MacCulloch<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>minuted his approval for M's request on<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="background-color: #FFFF00; ">1<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="background-color: #FFFF00; ">March</seg>
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>1870, but M did not receive the funds until June.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>This sum having recently been voted by the Legislation Assembly I beg now to ask,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Included in the Estimates for 1870, Chief Secretary,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Division 25, Miscellaneous<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>item No. 5,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>as 'Expenses in connexion with the transfer to the Queensland Government of the Dromedaries formerly obtained for Exploration purposes' (Victoria Parliament<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Parliamentary Paper 1870</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">,</seg>
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>no.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>B<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>2, p. 17), and approved in Parliament,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>26 May 1870 (<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Victoria Parliamentary Debates</seg>
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">'Hansard</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">'</seg>)), vol.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>10, p. 599.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>that you will be pleased to issue authority for the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="background-color: #FFFF00; ">pament</seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>of this sum.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir, your very obedient<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller C.M.G., M.D., F.R.S.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">The honorable</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir James McCulloch, Kn.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Chief Secretary.</p>
         </div>
